AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 392 House Bill No. 322*
by inserting the following new section immediately preceding the last section and renumbering
the subsequent section accordingly:
SECTION ___. It is not a violation of this act for an attorney licensed and
admitted to practice law, a department of justice accredited representative, or an
employee, volunteer, or other individual working under the direction of a licensed
attorney or a department of justice accredited representative to provide bona fide legal
advice to an individual whom the attorney knows or should have known has illegally
entered the United States, as determined by the bureau of immigration and customs
enforcement of the United States department of homeland security.
